1. Ja *idem* u bioskop večeras. (I am *going* to the cinema tonight.)
2. U bioskopu sam gledao sjajan film sinoć. (*Last night*, I watched a great movie at the cinema.)
3. Da li si *video* da je novi bioskop otvoren u centru grada? (Have you *seen* that the new cinema has opened in the city center?)
4. Ona voli da gleda filmove u *dobrom* bioskopu. (She likes to watch movies in a *good* cinema.)
5. Bioskop je bio prepun ljudi kada smo stigli. (The cinema was full of people when we arrived.)
6. Karte za bioskop su veoma skupe ovih dana. (Cinema tickets are very expensive these days.)
7. Sjajna vest je da će se na festivalu prikazati novi film iz našeg bioskopa. (The great news is that a new movie from our cinema will be shown at the festival.)
8. Ukoliko dođete ranije, možete da popijete kafu u kafiću koji se nalazi pored bioskopa. (If you come early, you can have coffee in the cafe next to the cinema.)
9. Bioskop je idealno mesto za izlazak sa prijateljima. (The cinema is an ideal place to go out with friends.)
10. Nisam siguran da li ću gledati film na televiziji ili u bioskopu. (I'm not sure if I will watch the movie on TV or in the cinema.)